==Chapter I==
===Talking to King Narnode===
* '''Player:''' Hello there, King Narnode.
* '''King Narnode Shareen:''' Good of you to stop by, human.
* '''Player:''' How fares the kingdom today?
* {{tcond|If the player does not have the requirements to start the quest:}}
** '''King Narnode Shareen:''' Everything seems fine, as far as I can tell... I will let you know if there is any trouble.
** {{tact|end}}
* {{tcond|If the player has the requirements to start the quest:}}
** '''King Narnode Shareen:''' All is not well, [player name]. Despite having had Glough under close surveillance since the events on Ape Atoll, he has managed to escape the Stronghold.
** '''King Narnode Shareen:''' I know you have already done so much for our kingdom, but could you look into Glough's disappearance?
** {{topt|I'll help you look for Glough.}}
*** '''Player:''' I'll help you look for Glough.
*** '''Player:''' Any idea on where to start?
*** '''King Narnode Shareen:''' You should look anywhere Glough may have left behind clues of his whereabouts. I've already had my men search his home, but perhaps you can find something they missed.
*** '''Player:''' I'll get right to it.
*** {{tact|end}}
** {{topt|I'm busy at the moment.}}
*** '''Player:''' I'm busy at the moment.
*** '''King Narnode Shareen:''' Perhaps some other time, then.
*** {{tact|end}}

====Talking to King Narnode again====
* '''King Narnode Shareen:''' How are you getting on, [player name]?
* '''Player:''' What should I be looking for again?
* '''King Narnode Shareen:''' You should look anywhere Glough may have left behind clues of his whereabouts. I've already had my men search his home, but perhaps you can find something they missed.
* {{tact|end}}

===Investigating the tree in Glough's home===
* '''Player:''' I wonder who could have left this in Glough's home? The initials A.A. are embroidered into it.
* {{tact|end}}

===Talking to Anita===
* '''Player:''' Is this your handkerchief?
* '''Anita:''' Why, yes, it is. I must have left it behind somewhere...
* {{tbox|You return Anita's handkerchief - she looks as if she could use it.}}
* '''Player:''' Hi Anita.
* '''Anita:''' *sob* W-what do you want? *sob*
* {{topt|What's wrong?}}
** '''Anita:''' *sob* It's Glough... I fear for the worst!
** '''Player:''' What do you mean?
** '''Anita:''' I think he might be seeing someone else! *sob* I hadn't heard from him in a while, and so decided to give him a visit.
** '''Anita:''' At first, I thought there was nobody home... *sob* But then I heard... *sob*
** '''Player:''' Heard what?
** '''Anita:''' I've already said too much. *sob* The last time I helped you, Glough lost his job!
** {{topt|What do you care? He's seeing someone else!}}
*** '''Player:''' What do you care? He's seeing someone else!
*** {{tact|end}}
** {{topt|He might be in trouble, I could help.}}
*** '''Player:''' He might be in trouble, I could help.
*** '''Anita:''' I heard whispering coming from higher up in his tree! I managed to climb the first branch... *sob* But I'm not agile enough to get up to the highest level...
*** '''Anita:''' Do you really think he might have gotten into trouble? *sob*
*** '''Player:''' There's another level to his home?
*** '''Anita:''' *sob* There's nowhere else the voices could have been coming from... *sob* Please, climb up there and let me know what you find!
*** {{tact|end}}
* {{topt|Any idea where Glough is?}}
** '''Player:''' Any idea where Glough is?
** '''Anita:''' The last time I helped you... *sob* Glough lost his job!
** {{tact|end}}
* {{topt|Nothing, goodbye.}}
** '''Player:''' Nothing, goodbye.
** {{tact|end}}

===Searching fire remains===
* {{tbox|The fire has been recently extinguished, you find a half burned note in the ashes.}}
* {{tact|end}}

===Reading the mysterious note===
* '''Player:''' The note is blank... I'm not sure what I'm meant to be reading right now.
* {{tact|end}}

===Reading the scrawled note===
* {{tbox|The rest of the note has been destroyed by the fire.}}
* '''Player:''' I need to translate this before it's going to be of any use... Maybe the King can help.
* {{tact|end}}

====Reading the scrawled note again====
* '''Player:''' What could the note mean? I should show it to the King, he might be able to make some sense of it.
* {{tact|end}}

===Talking to King Narnode===
