===Talking to Auguste===
* '''Auguste:''' Hello, [player name]. It is good to see you again. My enterprise has grown since we last met. I've expanded all over Gielinor!
* '''Auguste:''' If you'd like to go to a new location, you will have to help fly the balloon again. Some of the routes are very dangerous!
* '''Auguste:''' But each route you complete will earn you Firemaking experience.
* '''Auguste:''' Once you've opened a route, it only costs 1 log of the corresponding type to travel there again, from any location you've already opened!
* '''Auguste:''' I have also hired assistants to watch over the balloons at each new location we go to. They will help you get where you want to go.
* '''Auguste:''' Do you want to use the balloon? Just so you know, some locations require special logs and high Firemaking skills.
* {{topt|Talk about Assistant Le Smith.}}
** '''Player:''' I'd like to talk about Assistant Le Smith.
** '''Auguste:''' What a coincidence, he just so happened to visit recently. What's this about?
** '''Player:''' I need to know about the route you taught him.
** '''Auguste:''' Ah... I insisted it was far too dangerous, nobody has attempted to make that journey before!
** '''Player:''' Where?
** '''Auguste:''' Ape Atoll...
** {{topt|Thanks for the information.}}
*** '''Player:''' Thanks for the information.
*** {{tact|end}}
** {{topt|Can you teach me the route?}}
*** '''Player:''' Can you teach me the route?
*** '''Auguste:''' Most certainly not! For all I know, I've already sent one of my finest pilots to his peril!
*** {{tact|end}}
* {{topt|quest=No|Talk about something else.}}

===Talking to King Narnode===
* '''King Narnode Shareen:''' How are you getting on, [player name]?
* '''Player:''' I've found evidence that Glough may have headed to Ape Atoll.
* '''King Narnode Shareen:''' How could this be?
* '''Player:''' Assistant Le Smith is involved, it appears he has flown them there.
* '''King Narnode Shareen:''' Agh! We were foolish to allow him to stay here after dismissing him from the glider regiment.
* '''Player:''' So, what should we do now?
* '''King Narnode Shareen:''' Glough must be working with the monkeys once again. Fortunately, the rest of the 10th squad remained on Ape Atoll after your previous mission, they have been keeping a close eye on Awowogei.
* '''King Narnode Shareen:''' Perhaps they will have spotted something out of the ordinary that could help indicate what Glough is doing.
* '''King Narnode Shareen:''' Glough is a threat to us all... I must hereby re-assign you to Ape Atoll, [player name]. Report to Sergeant Garkor on Ape Atoll for further orders.
* {{tact|end}}

====Talking to King Narnode again====
* '''King Narnode Shareen:''' I have given you orders, [player name]. Report to Sergeant Garkor on Ape Atoll for further instruction.
* {{tact|end}}

==Chapter II==
===Talking to Garkor===
* '''Garkor:''' Welcome back, [player name].
* {{topt|King Narnode has sent me.}}
** '''Player:''' King Narnode has sent me. I'm investigating the disappearance of Glough.
** '''Garkor:''' Glough... really? We've not had any indication that he has returned to Ape Atoll.
** '''Garkor:''' But we have been seeing a lot of activity from Awowogei and his commanders - I assumed the king would send someone soon enough.
** '''Player:''' Any idea what they're up to?
** '''Garkor:''' We're not entirely sure, he has been keeping a tight lid on his plans. I guess it could be tied to Glough's disappearance? Perhaps you could get more information from Awowogei directly...
** '''Garkor:''' He may be willing to share his plans with you, assuming you are disguised with a greegree, that is.
** {{topt|That sounds far too dangerous.}}
*** '''Player:''' That sounds far too dangerous.
*** '''Garkor:''' A member of the 10th squad should never back down in the face of adversity, come back when you're feeling up to the task.
*** {{tact|end}}
** {{topt|It's worth a shot.}}
*** '''Player:''' It's worth a shot.
*** '''Garkor:''' Good luck, [player name].
*** {{tact|end}}
* {{topt|What are you still doing here?}}
** '''Player:''' What are you still doing here?
** '''Garkor:''' My squad and I are still carrying out reconnaissance. Awowogei has been very occupied as of lately, could this have something to do with why you're here?
** {{topt|I'm only passing through.}}
*** '''Player:''' I'm only passing through.
*** {{tact|end}}
** {{topt|King Narnode has sent me.}}
*** {{tact|above}}
* {{topt|I'm only passing through.}}
** '''Player:''' I'm only passing through.
** {{tact|end}}

