* '''Garkor:''' Have you learned anything from Awowogei yet?
* '''Player:''' Not yet...
* '''Garkor:''' We can't give up, [player name], come back when you've got more information.
* '''Player:''' I'll get to it right away.
* {{tact|end}}

===Talking to Awowogei===
* '''Awowogei:''' What do you want? I'm very busy right now.
* {{topt|How are things going, Awowogei?}}
